# IMDb Movies Data Analysis

## Objective
To analyze IMDb movie data using SQL and extract insights on movie ratings, genres, and popularity.

## Dataset
- Source: IMDb Movies Dataset
- Data includes movie title, genre, rating, votes, and year

## Key Analysis Performed
- Top-rated movies analysis
- Genre-wise movie distribution
- Average ratings by genre
- Filtering movies based on rating and votes

## SQL Concepts Used
- SELECT, WHERE
- GROUP BY, HAVING
- ORDER BY
- Subqueries
- Aggregate functions

## Tools Used
- MySQL
